snippet.title: A Space for The Unbound Trailer
snippet.description:
A Space for The Unbound is a slice-of-life adventure game with beautiful pixel art set in the late 90s rural Indonesia that tells a story about overcoming anxiety, depression, and the relationship between a boy and a girl with supernatural powers.

Coming soon
Wishlist the game here: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1201270/A_Space_For_The_Unbound/

Play the free chapter here: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1201280/A_Space_For_The_Unbound__Prologue/

Developed by Mojiken Studio
Published by Toge Productions
Music by Ittou's Soundworks
